{"tid":1392445,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[警醒］要控制好憤怒，係適當時間爆，努力同化敵人","createTime":"2019-07-31T17:54:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T01:01:45.000Z","uid":1882,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"20ea42b413ada7ce32d1cfde57f35ddb71780c0f","tid":1392445,"uid":1882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:54:02.000Z","msg":"日本例子<br />\n<br />\n民眾從喊「學生加油」變成罵學生「發狂」，商會成立民警自衛。主流社會從此把學生標籤為過激者。<br />\n<br />\n即使是年青人，也不再體恤年青人。作者引述了一名於後期入讀早稻田大學生的話，對上一代年輕人的抗爭批評得體無完膚：「那個世代真的進行過抗爭嗎？不就是自我感覺良好，說穿了不過只是讓體制小擦傷。他們不過是破壞物品，打傷人，製造麻煩了。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/international/日本社運失敗的歷史/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E7%A4%BE%E9%81%8B%E5%A4%B1%E6%95%97%E7%9A%84%E6%AD%B7%E5%8F%B2%2F&d=puaUx2dgpXXsrsLU9noyGFQKcmgIyYy1b1J%2Bn%2Bjwg5M%3D&h=1f0c7c7c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E7%A4%BE%E9%81%8B%E5%A4%B1%E6%95%97%E7%9A%84%E6%AD%B7%E5%8F%B2%2F&h=15879f3e\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/international/日本社運失敗的歷史/</a><br />\n<br />\n天琦<br />\n<br />\n你們或許因而心中充滿憤怒，這乃是人之常情，在危難中，仍要時刻保持警覺與思考。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我差唔多次次都有去發夢，都走過幾次前線。相信大家都知道有呢個問題。<br />\n<br />\n唔係講緊俾人打不還手，但大家遇到有人影相嗰時，問下對方有咩用意，人地唔肯刪除，配合先至爆發岀黎。<br />\n<br />\n遇到公公婆婆都禮貌少少，幫助佢地，就算佢哋唔係我哋呢邊，我哋都要解釋，唔好同佢地鬥大聲。要比佢哋尊重，令佢地知道，我哋唔係佢哋嘅敵人。當然如果佢哋出手另計啦，如果推人嘅，嘗試吓讓步，如果再激進啲直情打番佢啦要，但係過程千祈唔好俾人影相。<br />\n<br />\n我地要俾人知我哋係建設緊社會，我哋每行一步都要好小心，因為呢個係香港最後一次機會，失敗左共產黨唔會再有機會俾你試。<br />\n<br />\n憤怒係必須，係成個運動嘅推進力，一旦失控，只會係自毁長城。要切忌戀戰，每一次戰鬥係消耗緊人力，需要係重要時刻先至使用。<br />\n<br />\n民意係mp，我哋消耗緊嘅同時，亦要時刻補充。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我真係好唔想見到呢場運動會失敗。"},{"pid":"96647da684787ca10e5c75925afa8019b8888ba6","tid":1392445,"uid":101803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:57:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bc1dcebacf55173bb053ec5c1926ea9033519578","tid":1392445,"uid":1882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"96647da684787ca10e5c75925afa8019b8888ba6","tid":1392445,"uid":101803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:57:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:59:04.000Z","msg":"要時刻補充民意，不可以一直消耗。做係冇問題，但係要睇時機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41f896233e348e610c4f26954392ac33fdb2e394","tid":1392445,"uid":1882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:55:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfa748bf089893c6d4422638770a8dc4c175e2bd","tid":1392445,"uid":1882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:55:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0b81a810f6efe49bfc95d41e6fd4fffbe6cc6c8","tid":1392445,"uid":1882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:55:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea1b633d31c16a3a8a089cc528d18d018dadb44b","tid":1392445,"uid":233325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:56:30.000Z","msg":"唉"},{"pid":"b57de721ee1c0f6773daf85276d42a6c8a77c133","tid":1392445,"uid":1882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:56:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9874e977d0bdf3f4218ae6eaee348c1bdec3bd1e","tid":1392445,"uid":233325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:56:51.000Z","msg":"希望大家睇睇"},{"pid":"200eba6b11d618d4f91018ea4c7a219bfa242b7b","tid":1392445,"uid":1882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:57:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"719f21322212083109c3a9284662cb1cc85036cb","tid":1392445,"uid":1882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid